{"tid":2025204,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友好大食點算好。。","createTime":"2020-05-20T05:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T06:54:24.000Z","uid":3204,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7f01924f3a7d97e24acb3c4e2301845520cea8","tid":2025204,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"同現任已經四年幾，三十出頭但佢性需求有增無減，比岩岩拍拖個陣仲大食咗。<br />\n<br />\n每次見面都會性騷擾我，人少既地方又會直接伸手入黎，係街一冇人就好似奉旨咁會搞我同想出火。我對野外露出冇好感同好驚，但都畀佢試過係野外同交通工具到口同手。所以有時都同佢開房好過係街擔驚受怕，通常我地會揀正常酒店過夜會舒服啲，但佢開房就仲嚴重，晏晝check in 一次，夜晚一次，check out 前又一次，我前面後面同個口同對手幾勁都頂唔順啦。<br />\n<br />\n點解佢越老越大食？有冇其他男人都係咁？我就明顯比後生收斂咗好多。"},{"pid":"688a977b3529fa0663e7f680fd02e6c1a4d8d8d4","tid":2025204,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a797a694f4784a6b0781075f6aee006e1cf927","tid":2025204,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"688a977b3529fa0663e7f680fd02e6c1a4d8d8d4","tid":2025204,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2c989c3be25f05ede7f5eb9f1f48c67929d6ee","tid":2025204,"uid":129619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"GAY到"},{"pid":"fcba47c4ff68f85ef6d91156a40a6b577c9d2aa9","tid":2025204,"uid":10290,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"我屌<